  (text "DISPLAY INTERFACE NOTES:\\nSPI2 (LCD_CAM peripheral) 4-wire SPI 80MHz:\\n  GPIO17=LCD_CLK GPIO18=LCD_MOSI GPIO11=LCD_CS GPIO16=LCD_DC\\n  No MISO — display is write-only\\nGT911 CAPACITIVE TOUCH:\\n  I2C address: 0x5D (INT pulled HIGH before RST released)\\n  Shared I2C bus with ES8388 (addresses 0x10/0x11) — no conflict\\n  INT GPIO44: input-only — correct for interrupt-driven touch\\n  RST GPIO43: shared with LCD_RST — reset sequence handles both\\nBACKLIGHT: GPIO46 PWM via LEDC (5kHz 8-bit recommended)\\n  +5V_BL from +5V_EXT rail. C21 10µF bulk for LED inrush.\\nJP1 (0Ω populated): SPI clock routing default path\\nTarget module: Waveshare 5in SPI LCD 800x480 + GT911 cap touch\\nFPC: Molex 503480-2200. ENIG finish required. 0.5mm pitch."
    (at 30 145 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top))
    (uuid "529e6782-ab8d-4a72-b2d6-18f9dfe469f4")
  )
